  TaN lang5 na7 liu5-sim lai5 thak8 chiu7 tek-khak oe7 seng5-kong; kho2-sioh hian7-si5 kau3-hoe7-lai7 cheng-kong ti7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 lang5 si7 put-chi2 chio2, m7-na7 m7-bat Tiong-kok-ji7 e5 lang5 hiam5-oh m7-ai3 thak8, chiu7 u7 hak8-bun7 e5 lang5 iah8 m7-ai3 thak8, in-ui7 i phah-sng3 thak8 Tiong-kok-ji7 koaiN3-si3, thak8-liau2 ho2-thiaN koh chiaN5-ku3, na7 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 tioh8 hou, tioh8 tau3, iah8 oh-tit chiaN5-ku3, tui3 an2-ni m7-ai3 thak8. Che si7 tui3 i bo5 tui3-tiong7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 ian5-kou3, tok8-tok8 bo5-siuN7 thak8 Tiong-kok-ji7 tioh8-eng7 chap8-goa7-ni5 e5 kang-hu,siat-su2 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 na7 kam-goan7 chhin-chhiuN7 thak8 Tiong-kok-ji7 chap8-hun7 chit8-hun7 e5 tioh8-boa5, tek-khak oe7 khah-iaN5 thak8 Tiong-kok-ji7 e5 sek8 .
