  Lun7 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 hoat-tou7. TaN lang5 na7 beh oh8 tak8-hang7 e5 tai7-chi3 . tek-khak tioh8 tai7-seng beng5 i-e5 hoat-tou7, oh8-liau2 chiah oe7 chiaN5, bo5 tit-tioh8 hoat-tou7--e5, sui-jian5 ai3-oh8, kau3-be2 iah8 oh-tit chiaN5 . 
  Chhin-chhiuN7 an2-ni, lang5 beh thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7, kap sia2 peh8-oe7-ji7, iau3-kin2 tioh8 tai7-seng beng5 hit-e5 hoat-tou7, khoaN3 thau5-su7 sou2-lun7 chit-e5 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 iau3-kin2 ; sui-jian5 si7 put-chi2 kan2, chong2-si7 ki5-tiong u7 un2-bi5 e5 hoat-tou7, lan2 m7-thang khoaN3-khin; iau3-kin2 tioh8 soe3-ji7 kang2-kiu3 kau3 beng5, jian5-au7 hak8-sip8, chiah ng3-bang7 oe7 cheng-kong . 
  TaN u7 si3-hang7 pai5-liat8 ti7 e7-toe2. Te7-it-hang7, tioh8 jin7-beng5 ji7-bu2. Te7-ji7-hang7, tioh8 hun-piat8 pat-im, thau5-im bo5 ki3-ho7; te7 -ji7-im, eng7 chit8-phiat choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ¡¬ ¡¨ ; te7-saN-im, eng7 chit8-thoa choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ¡B ¡¨ ; te7-si3-im, eng7 si3-ji7 he7 ti7 be2-ji7 choe3 ki3-ho7,chiu7-si7 h, k, p, t ; te7-gou7-im, eng7 jin5--ji7 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ^ ¡¨ ; te7-lak8-im si7 kap te7-ji7-im saN-tang5 ; te7-chhit-im, eng7 chit8-uih8 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ -¡¨ ; te7 poeh-im, eng7 chhin-chhiuN7 te7-si3-im, koh ke chit8-kia7 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ | ¡¨ . TaN chit-e5 te7-ji7-hang7, mia5 sui-bong2 u7 pat-im sit8-chai7 na7 u7 chhit-im tiaN7-tiaN7, in-ui7 te7-ji7 kap te7-lak8 nng7-im saN-tang5. Te7-saN-hang7 si7 saN-tau3 e5 ki3-ho7, khi2-thau5 eng7 nng7-ji7 tau3-choe3 chit8-ji7, kiam2-chhai2 eng7 saN, si3, gou7 ji7 tau3-choe3 chit8-ji7 iah8-u7 chong2-si7 lang5 tioh8 jin7-sek, khoaN3 bou2-ji7 tau3 bou2-ji7 si7 sim2-mih8 ji7, chit8-e7 khoaN3-kiN3 chiu7 oe7 jin7-tit, long2 bian2-eng7 chhiat-im lai5 hou. Tioh8 oh8 kau3 an2-ni, chiah-thang sng3 si7 bat peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 lang5. Te7-si3-hang7, si7 tioh8-beng5 tak8-ho7 e5 ki3-ho7, in-ui7 u7 khi2-ku3 kap lang5-mia5 toe7-ho7-mia5 e5 ki3-ho7, long2 tioh8-eng7 toa7-pun2 e5 ji7 he7-ti7 thau5-ji7 lai5 hun-piat8 i. Koh u7 kau3-ku3 be7 kau3-chat, si7 eng7 chit8-tiam2 koah u7 thoa-be2 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§, ¡¨ koh u7 kau3-chat iau2-be7 kong2 beng5-pek8 i-e5 tai7-chi3--e5, si7 eng7 teng2-bin7 chit8-tiam2, e7-bin7 chit8-tiam2 koah u7 thoa-be2 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ; ¡¨ ; koh u7 kau3-chat i2-keng kong2 beng5-pek8 i-e5 tai7-chi3--e5, si7-eng7 chit8 iN5-tiam2 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ . ¡¨ ; koh u7 saN-lian5-ku3 put-lun7 nng7-ji7 a2-si7 saN-ji7, si7 eng7 chit8-uih8 ti7 tiong-ng choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ -¡¨ ; koh u7 oe7-be2, si7 eng7 nng7 sio2-uih8 he7 ti7 be2-ji7 e5 tiong-ng choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§--¡¨ ; koh u7 mng7-e5 ki3-ho7, si7 eng7 chit8-oan-khia7, e7-bin7 ke chit8-tiam2 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ? ¡¨ ; koh u7 ki5-khoai3 kap thou2-khui3, si7 eng7 chit8 tit8-khia7, e7-bin7 ke chit8-tiam2 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ! ¡¨ ; koh u7 in2 seng3-chheh [a2-si7 pat8-ho7 e5 chheh] e5 oe7, thau5 eng7 nng7-tiam2 koah thoa-be2 kau-khi2, be2-bin7 eng7 nng7-tiam2 koah thoa-be2 kau-loh8 choe3 ki3-ho7, chhin-chhiuN7 ¡§ ¡¨ . TaN lang5 na7 chit-e5 hoat-tou7 liu5-sim khi3-oh8, chai chaiN2-iuN7 tioh8-khi2, chaiN2-iuN7 tioh8-soah, u7 ji7 tioh8 thak8 khah-tang7, u7 ji7 tioh8 thak8 khah-khin, thak8-kau3 sek8-sek8, chiu7 thak8 chit-e5 peh8-oe7-ji7 pi2 thak8 Tiong-kok-ji7 khah ho2-thiaN, i3-su3 iah8 khah koe7-beng5 .
  Lun7 kau3 sia2-ji7 iah8 si7 an2-ni, tui3 an2-ni khoaN3, peh8-oe7-ji7 sit8-chai7 u7 toa7 li7-ek, lan2 kiam2 m7-tioh8 tui3-tiong7 liu5-sim lai5-oh8 mah ? 
  [Cheng5 te7-it, te7-ji7, te7-saN tiuN e5 Kau3-hoe7-po3, u7 in3 Iap8 Bok8-su sou2-cho3 lun7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 li7-ek. TaN chiong Lau5 Bou7-chheng te7-ji7-mia5 e5 lun7 in3 ti7 chia hou7 lin2 thak8 . I sou2 cho3-e5 khah-te2, sou2-i2 thang cho3-chit8-e7 in3 . ] 
  ThiN-e7 tak8-kok e5 ji7 bo5 long2 siang7-khoan2; tau3-ti2 long2 u7 lou7-eng7; taN che3 peh8-oe7-ji7 ia7 si7 bun5-ji7-tiong e5 chit8-lui7, i-e5 li7-ek lang5, pi2 pat8-ho7 e5 ji7, iau2 u7 khah-kin2 khah-khoai3 . TaN chiong i-e5 lou7-eng7 tai7-liok8 lai5 kong2 ti7 e7-te2 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 pang-chan7 kau3-hoe7 heng-ong7, tu2-tioh8 khun2-tiok8 be7 hoe3-bo5 . Kau3-hoe7 sou2-i2 bo5 heng-ong7, in-ui7 jip8-kau3 e5 lang5 bo5 chhim-chai to7-li2; bo5 chhim-chai to7-li2, in-ui7 ka-ti7 be7-hiau2 thak8 Seng3-keng; be7-hiau2 thak8 Seng3-keng, in-ui7 m7-bat ji7 . Khong2-chu2-ji7 oh ke2-soeh, na7 bat bo5 chhim, iu5-goan5 khoaN3 be7-lai5; kan-ta thiaN Sian-siN kong2, chiu7 sou2 bat--e5 iu2-han7, bo5 thiaN-tioh8--e5 chiu7 m7-chai; thiaN ku2--e5 iu7 be7 ki3-tit, ho5-hong3 u7 si5 hou7-lai5 chui2-chhim chou2-tong3; se3-su7 kiau2-jiau2, peN7-thiaN3 chou2-gai7, be7-e7 tak8 le2-pai3 long2 kau3 le2-pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2 ? ThiaN to7-li2 e5 lang5 na7 kheng2 khin5 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7, chiu7 chit8-ni5-ku2 put-lun7 lam5-hu7 lo2-iu3 long2 e7 ka-ti7 thak8 Seng3-keng, khah chai to7-li2; m7-bian2 theng3-hau7 kau3 pai3-tng5 thiaN to7-li2, ti7 ke-lai7 cha2-am3 ia7 thang thak8, tit-tioh8 li7-ek. Koh u7-si5 tu2-tioh8 chou2-tong3 be7 tang3 kau3 pai3-tng5 siu7 ka3-si7, chiu7 thang ka-ti7 khoaN3 chhian2-beng5 to7-li2 e5 chheh, iuN2-chhi7 sim-sin5, ia7 e7 li7-ek thiaN e5 lang5. Kau3-hoe7 e5 lang5 na7 bo5 khoaN3-khin peh8-oe7-ji7, tek-khak e7 na2-ku2 na2-toa7 chin3-pou7. Koh thiaN-kiN3 A-hui-li7-ka e5 tang-peng5 u7 chit8-e5 hai2-su7, mia5 Ma2-tat8-ka-su-ka, ti7 hia kau3-hoe7 tu2-tioh8 khun2-tiok8, ji7-gou7-ni5-ku2 bo5 Bok8-su ti7-teh ; kau3 khun2-tiok8 soah, Bok8-su koh khi3, khoaN3-kiN3 sin3 Chu2 e5 lang5 pi2-cheng5 koh khah-che7; chiu7-si7 in-ui7 u7 pun2-te7 e5 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 Seng3-chheh ti7-teh, lang5 e7 hiau2 ka-ti7 thak8. Che thang pin5-ki3 kau3-hoe7 e5 lang5 m7-thang bo5 thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 lu2-jin5 u7 ti3-hui7 . Hu7-jin5-lang5 e5 chai5-tiau7 bo5 khah-su ta-pou-lang5, sou2-i2 e7 bo5 hak8-bun7, in-ui7 Khong2-chu2-ji7 oh-thak8 . Na7 boeh thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7, tui3 lak8-hoe3 kau3 chap8-hoe3 si3-ni5 e5 ku2, chiu7 bo5 be7-hiau2-sia2 e5 ji7, iah8 bo5 be7-hiau2-thak8 e5 chheh ; an2-ni kiam2 m7-si7 chin toa7 e5 lou7-eng7?
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 tak8-teng2 cho3-kang e5 lang5 e7 hiau2 thak8 Seng3-chheh, kap chai che7-che7 hang7 e5 tai7-chi3. Tak8-teng2 cho3-kang e5 lang5 tak8-jit8 u7 kang tiN5-poaN3, iau2-ku2 na7 boeh thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 un2-tang3 e7 khi2-lai5. Goa2 khoaN3 hian7-si5 teh thiaN to7-li2--e5 khah-che7 si7 choh-sit kap chau2-than3 e5 lang5, pun2 m7-bat poaN3-ji7; tui3 thiaN to7-li2 chiaN3 tak8-pai2 An-hioh-jit8 oh8 thak8 ji7-bo2, tng tu2-a2 teh-thak8 e5 si5 m7-kaN2 siuN7 e7 bat, na7-si7 kau3-boe2 long2 e7 ka-ti7 thak8, m7-bian2 tiaN7-tiaN7 oa2-kho3 pat8-lang5 lai5 ka3 . Chiong-lai5 peh8-oe7-ji7 na2 che7 lang5 bat, chiu7 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 chheh ia7 e7 na2-chhut na2-che7 iuN7, kiam2-chhai2 Thian-bun5 Te7-li2 e5 chheh ; a2-si7 Soan3-hak8 Kek-but8 e5 chheh; Lek8-tai7 e5 tai7-chi3,tak8-kok e5 sin-bun5; che long2 e7 ke-thiN lang5 e5 ti3-hui7; an2-ni2-siN kiam2 thang kong2 peh8-oe7-ji7 m7-bian2 thak8 e7 cho3-tit ? 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 lang5 khah-khoai3 bat Khong2-chu2-ji7. Na7 seng thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 kau3 e7 sia2, ti7 thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7 e5 si5 hoan7 u7 m7-bat e5 ji7, kap be7-hiau2 ke2-soeh e5 i3-gi7; na7-sai2 mng7 sian-siN chit8-pai2, eng7 peh8-oe7-ji7 chu3 -beng5, chiu7 e7 ka-ti7 thak8, m7-bian2 kiaN koh be7 ki3-tit; an2-ni si7 thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7, ia7 tioh8 kiam eng7 peh8-oe7-ji7 . peh8-oe7-ji7 oe7 hou7 m7 bat thak8 Khong2-chu2-ji7 e5 lang5 bat Khong2-chu2-ji7. Goa2 sou2 bat e5 thoan5-to7 e5 lang5, lai7-tiong u7 nng7 lang5 chu7 soe3 bo5 thak8-chheh, kau3 ji7-chap8 chhut-thau5 he3 chiah thiaN to7-li2, oh8-thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7; hian7-si5 lian5 Tng5-lang5-ji7 e5 Seng3-chheh, kap sin-bun5 ia7 khoaN3 oe7 lai5: na7 m7 si7 bat peh8-oe7-ji7 thai3-tho2 u7 thang an2-ni?
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 lang5 khoai3 tu3-chheh. Lang5 na7 bat peh8-oe7-ji7 hoan7 u7 li7-ek lang5 e5 tai7-chi3, ai3 tu3-chheh po3 lang5 chai, thang sui5-siuN7 sui5-sia2; m7-bian2 hoan5-lo2 bo5 bun5-hoat, bo5 tiam2-ku3, hou7 lang5 iam3-chian7 m7 ai3 khoaN3 i sou2 tu3 e5 chheh . Iah8 e7 hou7 khoaN3-chheh e5 lang5 khoai3 beng5, m7-bian2 u7-e5 khoaN3 e7 beng5, u7-e5 khoaN3 be7-beng5 e5 chou2-gai7 . Na7 eng7 Khong2-chu2-ji7 tu3-chheh bo5 hiah khoai3, beh khoaN3 lang5 sou2 tu3 e5 chheh kau3 long2 beng5 ia7 si7 oh. M7 tat8-tioh8 peh8-oe7-ji7 hap8 nng7-peng5 e5 lang5 e5 li7-pian7.
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 san3-hiong-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 u7 ti3-hui7. San3-hiong-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 chai5-cheng5 be7 long2 khah-su ho2-giah8-lang5 e5 chu2-te7 ; kho2-sioh se3-han3 e5 si5 i bo5 thak8-chheh ; a2-si7 thak8 bo5 kui2-ni5 koh khi3 cho3-kang, kau3-boe2 u7 thak8 na2 bo5 thak8, iu5-goan5 m7-bat ji7. Peh8-oe7-ji7 na7 thak8 kau3 e7 sia2, chiu7 m7-bian2-kiaN e7 hui3-bo5-khi3, in-ui7 u7 ji7-bo2 thang chhiat-im, chit8-e7 hou, ji7 chiu7 ti7-teh ; khoaN3 beh kong2 sim2-mih8 oe7, siuN7 lai5 tau3 chiu7 u7 ji7, m7-bian2 chhin-chhiuN7 Khong2-chu2-ji7 u7 thak8-tioh8--e5 chiaN3 bat, bo5 thak8-tioh8--e5 chiu7 m7-bat . Koh tioh8 u7 thak8 koe3, chiaN3 chai hit-e5 kou3-tian2, bo5 thak8-koe3, chiu7 m7-chai hit-e5 in-iu5. Koh lang5 na7 beh bat Khong2-chu2-ji7 kau3 khoaN3 e7 lai5, sia2 e7 khi3, tioh8 tui3 se3-han3 tit8-tit8 thak8 kau3 chiaN5-chap8-ni5-ku2 chiaN3-e7, ia7 u7 kau3 chiaN5 chap8-ni5-ku2, kah i thak8 pun lang5 thiaN, kong2 be7 tit-lai5; u7 tai7-chi3 kah i ki3, sia2 be7 tit lai5. Peh8-oe7-ji7 m7-bian2 thak8 hiah-che7-ni5: m7-bian2 tui3 se3-han3 thak8 na7 kau3 bat, beh-thak8 beh-sia2 bo5 m7 sui5 -i3 . Kau3-hoe7-tiong e5 lang5 chiah8 kau3 saN-chap8-goa7-hoe3, si3-chap8-goa7-hoe3, gou7-chap8-hoe3 chiah oh8-thak8 peh8-oe7-ji7 e5 lang5 put-chi2 che7, koah-si7 kau3 sek8-sek8 e7 thak8 hou7 pat8-lang5 thiaN. U7 che3 peh8-oe7-ji7, san3-hiong lang5 e5 chu2-te7 m7-bian2 khou2 m7-bat ji7 . 
  Peh8-oe7-ji7 e7 hou7 bo5 siu7 kau3-hoa3 e5 lang5 piN3-cho3 u7 hak8-bun7; ku7-te2 bo5-ji7 piN3-kau3 u7 ji7. Cha2-jit8 lam5-iuN5 che7-che7 hai2-su7 bo5 siu7 kau3-hoa3; m7-bat le2-gi5, sim7-chi3 thai5-si2 lang5 soa3 chiah8-bah. Tui3 u7 Bok8-su khi3 thoan5 to7-li2, hak8-sip8 i-e5 thou2-im chhong3 peh8-oe7-ji7 ; tui3 an2-ni hong-siok8 toa7 pian3-oaN7, lang5 chiam7-chiam7 u7 ti3-hui7, kok-tou7 na2 -ku2 na2-heng ; kau3-hoe7 lang5-giah8 chit8-ni5 chit8-ni5 ke. M7-si7 peh8-oe7-ji7, thai3-tho2 e7 hou7 bo5 ji7 e5 sou2-chai7 piN3-cho3 u7 ji7, pian3-oaN7 kau3 hiah-kin2 ? Lan2 e5 Hong5-te3 chai soaN--nih8 e5 chhiN-hoan m7-bat le2-gi5, tiau5-ti5 siat gi7-oh8 chhiaN2 sian-siN lai5 ka3, tui3 siat kau3-taN chiong-kin7 peh-ni5-ku2; chha-put-to bo5 chit8-e5 bat-ji7 . In-ui7 ji7 kap oe7 bo5 siang7, tai7-seng kan-ta thak8 ji7-im long2 be7-hiau2 sim2-mih8 i3-su3, thak8-liau2 tioh8 koh ke2-soeh. Hiah-e5 chhiN-hoan e5 gin2-na2 kan-ta thiaN Sian-siN kong2, na2 chhin-chhiuN7 ah-a2 thiaN lui5, thiaN chit8-e5 siaN tiaN7-tiaN7. Phi3-ju7 na7 chiong peh8-oe7-ji7 hoan-ek8 in e5 im, thak8 in e5 oe7, tek-khak khah u7 eng3-hau7 .
  Goa2 chiau3 goa2 gu5-gong7 e5 i3-kian3, chiong peh8-oe7-ji7 kap Khong2-chu2-ji7 saN-pi2 lai5-lun7, m7-si7 hiam5 Khong2-chu2-ji7 bo5 lou7-eng7; put-ko3 kong2 peh8-oe7-ji7 khah khoai3 bat, hou7 lang5 khah-kin2 chin3-pou7 ; m7-bian2 kau3 ku2-ku2 tiaN7-tiaN7 hou7 ji7 pak8-teh . Iu7 koh hap8 ti7 lam5-hu7 lo2-iu3, pin5-chian7 hu3-kui3 tak8-teng2 e5 lang5 long2 thak8 e7 khi2. An2-ni kiam2 m7-si7 put-chi2 toa7 lou7-eng7? 
  Lang5 chun2-na7 bat Khong2-chu2-ji7 kau3 chin-chhim, na7 koh ke bat peh8-oe7-ji7, ia7-si7 ke chit8-hang7 e5 lou7-eng7. Kiam2 u7 lang5 hiam5 kong2 bat siuN-che7-iuN7-ji7 m7-ho2 mah ? 
  (Tai5-oan5 Hu2-siaN5 Kau3-hoe7-po3 te7 1~3,7 tiuN,1885 ni5 7~9 geh8,1886 ni5 2 geh8) 
